Package tetris

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Block
    A class for managing a Block and its location.
    Leaderboard
    A class for managing the in game leaderboard.
    Menu  
    Player
    A class for managing a player's name, unlocked levels, and high-scores.
    Playfield
    A class for creating a play field with a 2D grid of size height x width that can spawn in Tetrominos, and award points to the player when necessary.
    Tetris
    A class that houses the main method for the Tetris program.
    Tetromino
    A class for managing the Tetromino game pieces and handle their movement.
    UI
    A class for managing the in game menus.
